Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: China-US relations
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wy8n
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Feb 1983
Why the West Coast view of China differs from the capital's. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.